            android:text="If a fire does break out, don’t panic. If you throw water on the pan, grease could splatter and the fire might spread. Instead, grab a Fire Blanket and use it to smother the flames quickly. You can also grab a convenient Fire Extinguisher.\n\n
Smoke inhalation, not burns, is by far the largest killer in fires, so the more time you have to escape, the better.\n\n

Following these fire prevention tips and fire safety ideas will not only lessen your risk of damage, injury, and loss, but may also save your life, and the lives of your family. The minimal amount of time it takes to read and practice these fire prevention tips could end up being one of the best investments you ever make!
"
